The tools in this directory are used to interact with a coordinator node,
connected through a USB2Serial connected device.

The scripts use the python-xbee module, which can be obtained e.g. as such:

$ sudo pip install XBee

Running them looks like this:

$ ./dump.py
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
time    :  Sat, 29 Mar 2014 10:38:10 +0000
length  :  2
source  :  00 13 a2 00 40 8b 1a 6b / a4 af
options :  end-device acked
data    :  00 27
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
time    :  Sat, 29 Mar 2014 10:38:11 +0000
length  :  2
